00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.700
In this lesson, I will introduce the high level course concepts and learning objectives,

00:00:05.700 --> 00:00:08.490
review why this material is important,

00:00:08.490 --> 00:00:14.490
who is involved, then we compare today's systems to those of the past,

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:19.350
understanding some history, and tools and environments needed for this course.

00:00:19.350 --> 00:00:24.900
Finally, we'll wrap up with discussing the course project, and a recap.

00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:27.260
By the end of the lesson, you will be able to

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:30.905
understand how cybersecurity affects your life,

00:00:30.905 --> 00:00:35.125
describe how business stakeholders play a role in cybersecurity,

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:39.525
understand a brief history of information security and cybersecurity,

00:00:39.525 --> 00:00:42.110
understand high-level security tools,

00:00:42.110 --> 00:00:45.200
environments, and dependency, and lastly,

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:49.770
have a high level understanding of the course project.

